name: Landscaping Ep.! - Still Version 5K
description: This is my first mint based on my project "LandScaping" , that will be composed of a minimal still, and a animation realistically shaded for every Landscape/Episode. This one is the still version of the first episode. The compositions are made in 3d, realized from zero,then after being rendered with Vray (With very specific Render Elements), the 32 Bit-Depth images get post produced and adapted to work as intended in the classic 8 Bit-depth image.
